assetProfile.longBusinessSummary: Plaza Create Honsha Co.,Ltd. engages in the photography, video, and communication related businesses in Japan. It operates photo service shop under the Palette Plaza name; and photo studio under the Studio Palette name. The company also operates the carrier shops under the SoftBank, Ymobile, and Rakuten Mobile names; and provides Tsukurundesu (R), a DIY kit brand, as well as One-Bo, a personal meeting box that provides online meeting environment. Plaza Create Honsha Co.,Ltd. was incorporated in 1947 and is headquartered in Tokyo, Japan.
